{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"042e5ae4d1","title":"在中央工作会议上陈伯达发言时的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cda27e5ba5","index":0,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"042e5ae4d1"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"e44755a9df","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"括号内为陈伯达发言的有关内容。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e72b230787","type":"title","text":"在中央工作会议上陈伯达发言时的插话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"e44755a9df","type":"paragraph","text":"（主要矛盾是什么？主席根据大家的意见作了总结。主要矛盾是社会主义和资本主义的矛盾。“四清”与“四不清”不能说明问题的性质。封建社会就是清官与贪官的问题。《四进士》就是反贪官的嘛！）巡抚出朝，地动山摇，可了不起喱！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"2428f7e4ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（封建时代的清官实质上是假的。“三年清知府，十万雪花银。清，在不同社会有不同的阶级内容。资本主义社会也有所谓清官，那些清官都是大财阀。）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"7c669f570c","type":"paragraph","text":"清朝刘锣的《老残游记》中说，清官害人，比贪官害人还厉害。后来一查，南北朝史中的《魏史》就有此说。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"d2e74af9ff","type":"paragraph","text":"（内部矛盾哪个时代没有？党内党外矛盾交叉，党内有党。国民党也有此问题。）","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"7bcf3d8b4c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党内至少有两派，一个是社会主义派，一个是资本主义派。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"744366249f","type":"paragraph","text":"（主席强调，要听各方面的话。好话，环话，特别是反对的话要耐心听。这是工作做得好环的准则。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"a15e1c3df5","type":"paragraph","text":"讲话长了怎么办？李雪峰同志说的话，讲长了打零分。讲长了，让他讲长嘛！横直没人听嘛","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"a3bcd66104","type":"paragraph","text":"（许多人忘记自己是从哪里来的。不能忘本嘛！我这个人不参加革命，顶多是个小学教员、中学教员而已。）","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"4fe8121101","type":"paragraph","text":"大官是从小官来的，小官是从老百姓来的。我们都是从老百姓中来的，还是老百姓嘛！“蒋委员长”不姓将，姓郑，叫郑三发子，河南人氏，只知有母，不知有父，还不是老百姓变的？","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"8187a09783","type":"paragraph","text":"（主席常说，不要自以为是。乡干部当权，就以为自己的意见对。）","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"56ca3de949","type":"paragraph","text":"不要当了权，就是自己的意见对。自以为是，没有自以为不是的。为什么要升会？就是意见不一致。一致了开会十什么","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"8c6444bc8e","type":"paragraph","text":"（不怕管，只怕管嘛！）","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"},{"id":"e2daf1bd7a","type":"paragraph","text":"小官怕大官，大官怕洋人","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1"}],"page":{"id":"16c7b7764e","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"042e5ae4d1","start":352,"end":353}}}},"__N_SSG":true}